{"tid":613360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧卡古表弟衰強姦入獄5年","createTime":"2018-04-01T15:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T07:37:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"323f4e18245e365f25491bda41596e5e5e4b18f5","tid":613360,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/9/079/20910275079/20912980647_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F9%2F079%2F20910275079%2F20912980647_600x399.jpg&h=16586381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b2f97a9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】盧卡古的表弟出事！這名比利時rapper被判強姦罪成，入獄5年。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）今季以7500萬鎊從愛華頓加盟曼聯後，在周六英超對史雲斯轟入在英超第100個入球，同時是今季第26個入球，領軍以2:0取勝，事業如日方中。<br />\n<br />\n他的23歲表弟Nathan Ito Kavuanda本來也事業有成，以Cali這個藝名打滾音樂圈，是比利時著名hip hop組合ZwartWerk的成員。可是，他最近被安度爾法庭判處強姦罪成，入獄5年。<br />\n<br />\n案情披露，Cali跟其他ZwartWerk成員在2017年2月到安度爾滑雪時，晚上邀請了一群女生到他們的酒店房暢飲。當中一名女學生同意跟一名rapper上床，但其後有另一名男子，趁她睡覺時在梳化把她強姦，更有人用手提電話把拍下事件。<br />\n<br />\nZwartWerk的經理人本來希望用錢解決事件，但受害人拒絕。至於安度爾更爆料，指受害人曾被告知，同一名女生跟ZwartWerk所有成員發生性行為，是十分普通的事。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"9066024737283d60a070293f0fdb4675719020b3","tid":613360,"uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:29:25.000Z","msg":"魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f0e56709e09622248d3fdf237a2c4d5bf1af7a","tid":613360,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"至於安度爾更爆料，指受害人曾被告知，同一名女生跟ZwartWerk所有成員發生性行為，是十分普通的事。"},{"pid":"294877cb2af753af03450dae9957709ecc49da04","tid":613360,"uid":4496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58f0e56